3 ‚Äì Datatype: Matrices
A matrix is a two-dimensional array of numbers. It is created using the matrix() function:

#| '!! shinylive warning !!': |
#|   shinylive does not work in self-contained HTML documents.
#|   Please set `embed-resources: false` in your metadata.
#| standalone: true
#| viewerHeight: 280
